  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe Send/Bridge modal currently uses the same logic as the rest of the app:\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2023-02-06 at 11 01 09 AM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11161531/216998823-84d76851-9220-4ca1-a936-5f760a4d460c.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nInstead of that, it should use the following logic when the user enters an amount smaller than the resolution:\r\n- All instances related to the \"send amount\" (left side) should show as many decimal places as entered by the user\r\n- All instances related to the \"receive amount\" (right side) should show one more decimal place than what was entered by the user\r\n\r\n",
